    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of tree native to the northeastern United States, growing to 18 metres (59 feet) in height and having relatively large somewhat rounded, coarse-toothed leaves.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
